content.query:
select 
1 as SourceID,
'UUID'  as CatalogID,
newid() ActorID,
c.name as Actor,
 a.availabilitydate  as ReleaseDate,
a.Genre,
a.Rating,
cast(ReleaseYear as int) as  AvailabilityYear,
a.StreamingAvailabilityDate as AvailabilityDate,
a.Tier  as MovieTier,
a.Title as MovieTitle,
newid() over( PARTITION by a.title order by a.title )
 select * 
 from stg.movies_cosmosdb a
join stg.cosmos_actors c on a.Title=c.Title 
where a.title='Adventure Brick'
 ;
